\pard\f0\fs28   {\b 34. L. heterophyllus} L., {\i  Sp. Pl.} 733 (1753). Like {\b 33} but leaflets usually 2-3 pairs on upper leaves, and corolla 12-22 mm. 2n = 14. {\i   S.W. & C. Europe, extending to C. Sweden.} Au Cz Ga Ge He Hs It Lu Po Sa Su.
